        <section id="strategy">
          <h2>How to Trade Calendar Events</h2>
          <p>Not all events are created equal. Here's how to position around different catalyst types:</p>
          
          <h3>Exchange Listings</h3>
          <p><strong>Strategy:</strong> Buy 24-48 hours before expected listing. Sell the news within 6-12 hours of the listing announcement. Most of the gain happens in anticipation, not after.</p>
          
          <h3>Token Burns</h3>
          <p><strong>Strategy:</strong> Accumulate 2-3 days before the burn. The burn itself often generates a short-term pump as traders anticipate reduced supply. Sell 50% on the burn day, hold 50% for the post-burn momentum.</p>
          
          <h3>Fed Decisions / Macro Events</h3>
          <p><strong>Strategy:</strong> Reduce position size by 50% 24 hours before the event. Wait 12 hours after the announcement for the market to absorb the news. Re-enter once direction is clear.</p>
          
          <h3>Community Votes</h3>
          <p><strong>Strategy:</strong> Buy if the proposal is bullish (treasury allocation, buybacks, burns). Sell if the proposal is neutral or bearish. Votes are often preceded by weeks of discussion ” the price move happens when the vote is announced, not when it passes.</p>
          
          <div class="tip-box">
            <strong>�™� Calendar Pro Tip:</strong> Create your own meme coin calendar using Google Calendar or Notion. Set alerts 24 hours before each event. This gives you time to research and position yourself before the rest of the market reacts.
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="conclusion">
          <h2>The Bottom Line</h2>
          <p>A meme coin calendar is your edge. While most traders react to events after they happen, you can position yourself days or even weeks in advance. Bookmark this page ” we'll update it monthly as new events are confirmed.</p>
          <p>Remember: not every event will produce a profitable trade. But by knowing what's coming, you reduce surprise, remove emotion, and give yourself the single biggest advantage in meme coin trading: preparation.</p>
        </section>

